There were soo many rumors, one even had me trying to break up the Fellowship.  Making trouble for people was never my thing.  I knew for a fact that the Blades would likely leave the Fellowship before I offically applied, and long before I was tagged.  There was no malice, deception, or trickery.  Perhaps they tagged me a day early, hardly grounds for such a hub-ub.  They didn't tag me early to insult or trick anyone.  &lt;sigh&gt;<br>
