<br>
The fellowship resignation letter was not created hastily, it had been created by officers and leaders weeks before, and was - at the time when Hether, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>an ex-member</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, saw it fit to publicly discuss our decision in the Fellowship boards (where she had no right to be either, seeing as she was no longer a part of any Fellowship guild) - still under member's approval.  Her topic was the question 'are there any good guilds left' - how on earth she saw fit to tell about our impending internal changes had any bearings on that still boggles me, but seeing as she calls me a 'vociferous Hether-hater', I guess that's the reason why...<br>
<br>
We did have a majority agreeing to leaving the Fellowship and approving our letter of resignation, but were giving our guildies more time - not everyone can troll boards day in and day out.<br>
<br>
Yes, it was posted in haste once Hether jumped the gun on our decision, but in no means was it hastily assembled or approved just so we 'did the right thing'.  By maybe about a day or a weekend we were forced to post our resignation letter because of some ex-member's big mouth and because of one current member who had a tantrum (see original poster) about the way we were going with the guild.<br>
<br>
Anyways, please do not presume to know the right way of things, until you have at least gotten all the facts, which obviously you did not.<br>
<br>
As for Mhordel being guilded before we officially resigned - that was indeed a fault of ours, and it wouldn't have taken weeks nor months before we were to announce our departure like you seem to imply.  So much for your 'trust' in members of a Fellowship to which you belong.<br>
<br>
I think sometimes people need to get their facts straight before coming here and spewing stuff out they have no knowledge of.<br>
<br>
To each their own opinion, yet get the right of it before you slander others...<br>
<br>
Anyways, it's in the past, we made a decision, we took a different path, we didn't flame anyone, let it rest - I just wanted to set this straight.<br>
